@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Login rate limit (repeat this request >10 times within 1 minute from same IP to trigger 429)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "noone@example.com",
  "password": "wrong-password"
}

### Workshop manage-token rate limit (repeat this request >30 times within 1 minute from same IP to trigger 429)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop-bookings/manage/test-token
